@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Location | Adidop";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_LayoutProduct.cshtml";
}
<header class="border-b border-gray-900 pb-6 mb-8 mx-6 pl-1">
    <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-gray-500 uppercase mb-1">Fashion Knowledge & Chain System
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-black tracking-tight uppercase text-gray-900 mb-1">
        Franchise Policy
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold tracking-wide text-gray-700 uppercase">
        ADIDOP FOOTWEAR
    </p>
</header>

<div class="space-y-10 pl-1">

    <section class="space-y-2 mx-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">
            1. What is Franchise Business?
        </h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-3 ">
            <p>
                Franchise business (often called <span class="font-semibold text-gray-950">franchise</span>) is a
                network
                expansion system that provides products and services to the franchisee. It is an opportunity to grow a
                business under a brand with intellectual property rights licensed to the franchised entity.
            </p>
            <p>
                This model occurs when the franchisor grants the franchisee the right to use the brand and operating
                methods. In return, the franchisee must pay fees according to the agreed contract.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-2 mx-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">
            2. Franchise Brand: ADIDOP FOOTWEAR
        </h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-3">
            <p>
                In 2021, with dynamism, creativity, and by anticipating the development trends of streetwear combined
                with future sports technology, we began successfully building and delivering results with the ADIDOP
                FOOTWEAR franchise system in Vietnam.
            </p>
            <p class="italic border-l-2 border-gray-900 pl-4 text-gray-600">
                Coming to ADIDOP FOOTWEAR is not only about experiencing new spaces but also about sharing, empathizing,
                and proving a new fashion spirit.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4 mx-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">
            3. Costs and Franchise Terminology
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
                <span class="font-bold">Franchisor:</span> <span class="font-semibold text-gray-950">ADIDOP
                FOOTWEAR</span> is the party granting an entity or group the right to use its brand and business
                operation methods.
            </p>
            <p>
                <span class="font-bold">Franchisee:</span> The party receiving the rights to use the brand,
                operating methods, and business model from the franchisor. In return, the franchisee must pay the
                applicable franchise fees.
            </p>
            <p>
                <span class="font-bold">Franchise fee:</span> This is the fee the franchisee pays to the franchisor to
                use the brand, operating methods, and business model from the franchisor. The ADIDOP FOOTWEAR brand
                franchise fee is <span class="font-bold text-gray-950">300,000,000 VND</span> for a 3-year (36-month)
                contract. <span class="font-medium">OR SETUP & MANAGEMENT TRAINING FEE: 150,000,000 VND</span> (required
                with
                the franchise name accompanied by ADIDOP FOOTWEAR).
            </p>
            <p>
                <span class="font-bold">Initial Fee:</span> The initial cost for preparation and support to start
                business,
                such as basic construction, technology transfer, training, procedures, based on the service packages the
                franchisee wants, the scale of the franchisee, the complexity of technology transfer, and the
                operational
                scope in the franchisee's territory.
            </p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-950">
                Estimated initial investment cost ranges from 1,800,000,000 VND to 2,500,000,000 VND.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4 mx-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">
            4. Support from ADIDOP FOOTWEAR
        </h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-gray-700">

            <div class="space-y-1">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-950">About Construction:</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside pl-1 space-y-0.5">
                    <li>Design and decorate the store layout</li>
                    <li>Construction supervision</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-1">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-950">About Materials:</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside pl-1 space-y-0.5">
                    <li>Provide complete footwear products and warehouse machinery</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-1">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-950">About Recruitment and Training:</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside pl-1 space-y-0.5">
                    <li>Provide job description materials for positions</li>
                    <li>Provide operation manuals (SOP)</li>
                    <li>Train staff</li>
                    <li>Update professional knowledge as needed</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-1">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-950">About Marketing:</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside pl-1 space-y-0.5">
                    <li>Advise marketing strategies suitable to the area</li>
                    <li>Use system resources: Website, Fanpage, TikTok...</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

</div>
<section class="space-y-4 mt-9 mb-10 ">
    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl mx-6 font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">
        5. System Location Map
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mx-6">
        Our partners and customers can visit the headquarters or product experience stores at the locations below:
    </p>

    <div class="w-full h-64 sm:h-96 rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
        <iframe
            src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d62702.207331160556!2d106.59328100421772!3d10.819885568726985!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31752edb765b5c25%3A0x9a3519bdad5a85a3!2zVHLGsOG7nW5nIMSQ4bqhaSBo4buNYyBOZ2_huqFpIG5n4buvIC0gVGluIGjhu41jIFRow6BuaCBwaOG7kSBI4buTIENow60gTWluaCAoSFVGTElUKQ!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1780176419503!5m2!1svi!2s"
            class="w-full h-full border-0" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy"
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
        </iframe>
    </div>
</section>

